# Implementation Plan - Memo Feature & Bible Cleanup

## Goal Description
The user wants to add a Memo feature accessible from the main page (under Prayer) that supports checkboxes, toggles, pagination (5 items/page), and persistence. Additionally, the Bible text needs to be cleaned of `&#x27;` and `!` characters.

## Proposed Changes

### Bible Text Cleanup
